(firstQuint)Effect of a Nutritional Supplement on H&N Cancer Patients.

 H&N cancer patients will be randomized to receive either a nutritionally enhanced product or standard treatment.

 The patients in both groups will receive nutritional counseling weekly by the RD.

 Anthropometric measures, available lab values, mucositis grade, and quality of life measures will be compared between groups.

